snippet.title: Nelly Cootalot: The Fowl Fleet - Launch Trailer - English
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam for Windows Mac & Linux! http://store.steampowered.com/app/317320 

Pirate heroine Nelly Cootalot takes on the villainous Baron Widebeard in this point and click adventure game. Meet a cast of outlandish characters and face perplexing challenges in your quest for the Treasure of the Seventh Sea.

Also available from other stores: http://www.nellycootalot.com/the-game/buy-now
